ear went back to every 8 hours it would solve 99% of the conflict between players in different prime time playing hours.<br>
<br>
Rather than arguing with each other why not take this up in person with VI at the Fan Faire.  Those of us attending the fan faire must bring up the issue and explain the problem and how it disenfranchises a large number of players.  Those of us not attending the fan faire can show our support by posting to the official EQ board and sending Emails to VI staff.<br>
<br>
Lets work together to bring about a solution that we already know will make everybody happy.  Write an e-mail today.  If you are attending the Faire I'll see you in Minneapolis.  I'll be the one requesting a return to 8 hour pops. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unaida.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Naida</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br> <font color=#CC9900>(6/13/01 8:24:53 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re:  Raid Shedules, spawn cycles and Fan Faire  </span><hr size=1> I think this is a good idea. One of the best ways to help solve the issues with the differences in time zones and spawn cycles is to change the spawn cycle.<br>
<br>
So, what email addresses do we write to?<br>
 <p>Naida That<br>Cleric of Evoluxa</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uiullaanya.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Iullaanya</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br> <font color=#CC9900>(6/13/01 8:51:33 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re:  Raid Shedules, spawn cycles and Fan Faire  </span><hr size=1> Well actually that would work in fear, but not in Hate if you are trying to do second floor.  At least for most people. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uveldanlionsfury.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Veldan Lionsfury</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Traveller of Underfoot</span><br> <font color=#CC9900>(6/14/01 7:10:14 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re:  Raid Shedules, spawn cycles and Fan Faire  </span><hr size=1> What do you mean 'back' to 8 hours?  They used to spawn faster? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/urelbeekeinre.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Relbeek Einre</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>uncommonly Good <img src=http://www.brellserilis.net/images/goldstartr.gif align=middle></span><br> <font color=#CC9900>(6/14/01 8:03:40 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.tigerden.com/~twilight/keebler-60x60.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re:  Raid Shedules, spawn cycles and Fan Faire  </span><hr size=1> No, no, he meant scale repop time back to 8 hours as opposed to forward to 16 hours. You get the idea. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ufettenmysteblayde.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fetten Mysteblayde</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br> <font color=#CC9900>(6/16/01 11:48:26 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re:  Raid Shedules, spawn cycles and Fan Faire  </span><hr size=1> That is a great idea but you would need to convince the non-US guilds to participate in that emailing. However 8 hours is a little fast, I think 10 would be better. Even so I'm sure most guilds and raid leaders out there now could adjust accordingly.<br>
<br>
<br>
Fetten Mystebladye<br>
Ranger of Nocturne Mist  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utwiggietymberwolf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Twiggie Tymberwolf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot <img src=http://www.brellserilis.net/images/goldstartr.gif align=middle></span><br> <font color=#CC9900>(6/17/01 12:18:05 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re:  Raid Shedules, spawn cycles and Fan Faire  </span><hr size=1> IF they did move it back to 8 hours expect them to scale back the drop rate accordingly.  Maybe this isn't a bad thing, maybe it is. You could easily get 2 raids in on Saturday and Sunday if it was 8 hours.  For Fear start at 10 am and clear the plane.  Take a dinner break. The plane would start repop at 6pm.  Begin to clear again.  Plane would repop again at 2am and be fully popped by the time the Sunday crew came in.  With an 8 hour repop it would solve all the time zone issues since a weekday raid that starts at 6pm pst would start repops at 2am allowing 2 hours of repops before Zenith or another asian guild would even start.  <br>
I think the only way to get them to scale back the repop to 8 hours (a ~40% reduction in spawn time) would be to reduce the drop rate of the armor by the same amount.  They aren't going to just increase the spawn rate.  <p><table>
